### 监听详细下载进度

```kotlin
helper.downloadVideo(videoInfo, format, outputDir) { progress ->
    when (progress.status) {
        DownloadProgress.Status.DOWNLOADING -> {
            val percent = progress.percentage
            val downloaded = formatFileSize(progress.bytesDownloaded)
            val total = formatFileSize(progress.totalBytes)
            val speed = formatSpeed(progress.speed)
            println("下载中: $percent% ($downloaded / $total) 速度: $speed")
        }
        DownloadProgress.Status.MERGING -> {
            println("正在合并音视频...")
        }
        DownloadProgress.Status.COMPLETED -> {
            println("下载完成!")
        }
        DownloadProgress.Status.FAILED -> {
            println("下载失败")
        }
    }
}
```

